GET /tickets-main/_search
{
  "size": 0,
  "query": {
    "term": {
      "state.keyword": "DONE"
    }
  },
  "aggs": {
    "by_user": {
      "terms": {
        "field": "assignee_username.keyword",
        "size": 10
      },
      "aggs": {
        "tickets": {
          "top_hits": {
            "_source": ["id", "title", "state"],
            "size": 100,
            "sort": [
              { "updated_at": { "order": "desc" } }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}


pozn.: top-hits z agregaec umožní přímo vypsat záznamy